headline: Elliott Releases Bonus Episode of "Streamline 66" Podcast Series Featuring 1:1 Conversation with Partner John Pike
summary: Elliott Investment Management L.P. ("Elliott"), which manages funds that together make it a top five shareholder in Phillips 66 (NYSE: PSX) (the "Company" or "Phillips"), today released the third episode of the Streamline 66 Podcast. The series features 1:1 conversations with Elliott's highly qualified director nominees, as well as industry experts.
